### 1. Run Evaluation for User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/evaluations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 2,
  "period": "2026-Q1"
}

### 2. Get Evaluation by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/evaluations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Evaluations by User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/evaluations/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Run Evaluation again (idempotent - should update)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/evaluations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "period": "2026-Q1"
}

### 5. Run Evaluation for non-existent user (404)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/evaluations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 999,
  "period": "2026-Q1"
}

### 6. Run Evaluation with missing fields (400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/evaluations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": null,
  "period": ""
}